    About us

    Chocomans has been serving Chennai for the last 10 years with delectable cakes and excellent service. We are a team of professionals with 25 years of hospitality experience dedicated to providing our cakes with the best possible quality and flavour. Our experience and commitment to perfection have made us into the business we are today. Our irresistible and mouth-watery quality cakes are bound to tempt you.

    We are dedicated to offering our patrons a top-tier quality product alongside outstanding service. Our cakes are crafted from a multitude of the finest ingredients and are prepped with care and attention to detail by our seasoned team so that you will receive a product that is not only delicious but also looks fabulous. Our passion is to delight you with our cakesfor any occasion.

    If you are in Chennai, please stop by and see us! We would love to serve you.

    Why Choose Chocomans?

    There are many reasons to choose our bakery. Still, three stand out: our passion for baking, our commitment to using only the highest quality ingredients, and our 10+ years of experience in the bakery industry.

    Our passion for baking means we love what we do and take pride in every product we create. We believe that the best-baked goods are made with the best ingredients, which is why we only use the highest quality ingredients in our recipes.

    Our 10+ years of experience in the bakery industry allow us to offer our customers a wide range of products, from cakes and cookies to loaves of bread and pastries. We also have a team of highly skilled and experienced bakers who are dedicated to creating delectable delicacies to make your day more memorable.

    In a city like Chennai, which is bustling with activity all day, finding time to attend social gatherings or even celebrate special occasions with your loved ones can be challenging. Our online cake delivery service is the perfect solution if youre looking for a hassle-free way to order a cake for your memorable event.

    If you are looking for a delicious and safe cake, look no further than our shop. We are FSSAI certified, meaning our cakes are made per the highest food safety standards.

    Our cake shop offers a 500+ variety of appealing designer cakes, each more delicious than the last. With over 40+ irresistible flavours to choose from, were sure to have the perfect cake for any of your occasions; whether celebrating a birthday, anniversary or just because, our cakes will make your event extra special.

    Our team of skilled cake artists can create custom cakes to order. We also offer the best online cake delivery service in Chennai, so you can be sure your cake will arrive fresh and on time. Our customers are our top priority, and were proud to have served over 1 Million happy customers. Were the perfect choice for your celebration!

    We offer Eggless cakes.

    Nowadays, more and more people are considering vegetarianism for ethical, environmental, or health reasons. As a result, the demand for Eggless cakes has increased. If youre looking for a delicious Eggless cake, look no further weve got you covered!

    At our bakery, we offer a wide variety of eggless cakes that are perfect for any occasion. Whether youre looking for a birthday cake, a Wedding cake, or just a simple dessert, we have an eggless option that will suit your needs.

    Our eggless cakes are made with the same dedication and attention to detail as our regular cakes. We use only the finest ingredients, and our bakers are passionate about creating the perfect Eggless Cake for every customer.

    No More Stress! We Made It Easier And Hassle Free To Order Eggless Cakes. Now Your Eggless Cakes Are Just A Click Away. Our service allows you to browse through various delicious, contemporary cake designs. Order your favourite one and make it eggless by clicking the eggless option. Enjoy the perfect cake for any occasion by getting it delivered to your doorstep.

    Rasamalai Cake, Gulab Jamun Cake, Motichoor Cake – All Delicious, Desi and Eggless! Try our bestselling eggless cakes with unique flavours like Rasamalai, gulab jamun, and Motichoor, which will tantalise your taste buds.

    Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)

    1. How long will the cake remains good?

    Our cakes will remain suitable for up to 24 hours with refrigeration.

    2. Can I get home delivery?

    Yes. With dedicated delivery executives, We offer doorstep delivery all over Chennai.

    3. How long can a cake be kept outside without refrigeration?

    Our fondant cakes remain fresh for 1 hour without refrigeration, and other cakes remain suitable for 30 minutes after delivery.

    4. Does Chocomans use gelatin in cakes?

    No! Our cakes are 100% gelatin free.

    5. Do You have any add-ons with birthday cakes?

    Yes, We offer Party Poppers, Number Candles, Magic Candles, Musical Flower Candles, Party Caps, Sparkling candles and snow spray. While placing an order for cake, you get an option to select your add-ons by clicking the party items option.

    6. Do you take the same day orders as well?

    Yes. We provide same-day delivery to your doorstep. But same-day deliery is available only for select products.

    7. Do you customise cakes?

    Yes. We make custom designer cakes as per your requirement.
